{"content": "I need to multiply 502 \u00d7 255 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 502\u2081\u2081 to base 10**\n- 502\u2081\u2081 = 5\u00d711\u00b2 + 0\u00d711\u00b9 + 2\u00d711\u2070\n- = 5\u00d7121 + 0\u00d711 + 2\u00d71\n- = 605 + 0 + 2\n- = 607\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 255\u2081\u2081 to base 10**\n- 255\u2081\u2081 = 2\u00d711\u00b2 + 5\u00d711\u00b9 + 5\u00d711\u2070\n- = 2\u00d7121 + 5\u00d711 + 5\u00d71\n- = 242 + 55 + 5\n- = 302\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 607 \u00d7 302 = 183,314\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 183,314\u2081\u2080 to base 11**\n- 183,314 \u00f7 11 = 16,665 R 9\n- 16,665 \u00f7 11 = 1,515 R 0\n- 1,515 \u00f7 11 = 137 R 8\n- 137 \u00f7 11 = 12 R 5\n- 12 \u00f7 11 = 1 R 1\n- 1 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 1\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 115809\u2081\u2081\n\n**Answer: 115809**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 401}